trans-unit.source: Animates the value of a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Color"></xref> property along a set of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames*> over a specified <xref href="System.Windows.Duration"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: A key frame animation's target values are defined by its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A> property, which contains a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame> objects.
trans-unit.target: En nøkkel for animasjonen målverdier er definert av den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A>egenskap, som inneholder en samling av <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame> defines a segment of the animation with its own target <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame>definerer segmentet animasjonen med egne mål <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame>

trans-unit.source: When the animation runs, it progresses from one key value to the next at the specified key times.
trans-unit.target: Når animasjonen kjører, den går videre fra én nøkkelverdien til neste på den angitte nøkkelkolonner ganger.

trans-unit.source: There are three types of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame> classes, one for each supported interpolation method: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearColorKeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteColorKeyFrame>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineColorKeyFrame>.
trans-unit.target: Det finnes tre typer <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame>klasser, én for hver støttede interpoleringsmetode: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearColorKeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteColorKeyFrame>, og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineColorKeyFrame>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineColorKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteColorKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearColorKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame>

trans-unit.source: Unlike a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimation>, a ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames can have more than two of target values.
trans-unit.target: I motsetning til en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimation>, en ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames kan ha flere enn to målverdier.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimation>

trans-unit.source: You can also control the interpolation method of individual <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame> segments.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også kontrollere interpoleringsmetode over enkelte <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame>segmenter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame>

trans-unit.source: Calculates a value that represents the current value of the property being animated, as determined by this instance of <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the `defaultOriginValue` is the first in the composition chain, this value will be the snapshot value (if one is available) or the base property value; otherwise this value will be the value returned by the previous animation in the chain with an <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.AnimationClock> that is not <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Clock.Stopped%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `defaultOriginValue` er først i sammensetningen-kjede denne verdien være statisk utvalg-verdi (Hvis det finnes) eller base egenskapsverdien; Hvis denne verdien blir verdien som returneres av forrige animasjon i kjeden med en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.AnimationClock>som ikke er <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Clock.Stopped%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Clock.Stopped%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.AnimationClock>

trans-unit.source: The `defaultDestinationValue` is the base value if the animation is in the first composition layer of animations on a property; otherwise the value is the output value from the previous composition layer of animations for the property.
trans-unit.target: Den `defaultDestinationValue` er grunnleggende verdi Hvis animasjonen er det første sammensetning laget for animasjoner på en egenskap, hvis verdien er output-verdi fra den forrige sammensetningen lag med animasjoner for egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The suggested origin value, used if the animation does not have its own explicitly set start value.

trans-unit.source: The suggested destination value, used if the animation does not have its own explicitly set end value.
